{"tid":2289613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"慶中國國慶籌委會違規亂掛橫額 民政處稱不知情","createTime":"2020-11-17T11:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T11:36:34.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9fea6bd07f5cc18e32160833b30b04dfcc4f8b1","tid":2289613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"民主派自光復區議會後，各區大幅削減慶祝中國國慶活動的款項，惟荃灣區議會早前發現，該區雖拒批有關國慶活動申請，區內仍有多達30幅由「香港同胞慶祝國慶籌備委員會」及「荃灣各界人士」懸掛的違規橫額，民政處代表今午（17日）在區議會稱，地政署沒有批准相關活動申請，民政處亦將結果通知籌委會，強調民政處對擅掛橫額並不知情。<br />\n<br />\n陳稱，民政處當時已將地政處拒批有關活動申請的結果通知籌委會，而民政處是在有傳媒查詢後始知籌委會擅自掛該批橫額，事前並不知情，強調民政處其後已派員到場視察，並發現該批違規橫額已被移除。"},{"pid":"b5dfb5fd0171595dd9ed539fa6a7ae7cdc1d6d1d","tid":2289613,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:09:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/EJ2CV4Y75BHI5CUGHF2SPY4WZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FEJ2CV4Y75BHI5CUGHF2SPY4WZ4%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM49jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=a739d87e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FEJ2CV4Y75BHI5CUGHF2SPY4WZ4%2F&h=63258640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/EJ2CV4Y75BHI5CUGHF2SPY4WZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"6bb4a30f8cec546a97e5dbb715270b76ddd3f019","tid":2289613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f03662e58a6749fd18727c9bbf1dd8f21a5e2ec","tid":2289613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd417073182137eb3157e93fa8fbc7485029b3c","tid":2289613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\